description.plain:
Doechii is a rapper, singer, and songwriter from Tampa, Florida.

The artist first rose to popularity following the viral success on Tik Tok of her 2020 single “Yucky Blucky Fruitcake,” which led her to sign a record deal with the Los Angeles-based label Top Dawg Entertainment in 2021.

In August 2022, Doechii released her debut project with the label, the EP she / her / black bitch.
